data.description: Presidents' Day Price Slash! :)  Dropping $10,000 off this beauty for a quick smooth sale. Grab it before it's history!   Welcome to your new Move-in Ready & Recently Updated Home!    Welcoming Foyer, Spacious Dining Area, and Large Dream Eat-in Kitchen with breakfast nook, bar area; featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and spacious pantry.     The grand living room, divided into two zones and adorned with a cozy fireplace, offers the ideal backdrop for relaxation and entertainment.  A generous laundry room enhances convenience, while direct access to the fenced backyard opens to a private outdoor haven, complete with a patio and storage shed, ready for your new chapter!    4 Spacious bedrooms Upstairs. Master bedroom suite with a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom, showcasing a luxuriously tiled shower.   No HOA/POA fees; not in flood zone.  Secure your piece of the American dream before it’s signed, sealed, and delivered to someone else!
